::Mosquitor::

The bushes rustle, Mosquitor emerging and running up to Black Arachnia as she 
finishes her transmission.

"Leadership!" he says, saluting, "I have a new soldier for you!"

He looks behind him, not seeing Necro. "Somewhere here!" he says 
enthusiastically, starting to retrace his steps and look for Necro.
